<h2>Workflow</h2>

<p>If you have not used RTorrent before you and are used to gui's you will get a bit of shock when you first try to drive it. But help is close at hand for the userguide go <a href="http://libtorrent.rakshasa.no/wiki/RTorrentUserGuide">here</a></p>

